ts in this group\ncould be responsible for the production of Earth's transient irregular natural\nsatellites.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 13 May 2013 16:11:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 27 May 2013 08:09:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-09-25"}
