ented thermodynamic functions, which we\nbelieve will help to broaden the current research and pave a new way to\nmanipulate heat for novel device applications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 13 May 2013 17:43:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 16 May 2013 12:00:32 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 23 May 2013 01:32:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-11-25"}
