y reduce the effects of thermal feedback.\nTo the best of our knowledge, this potential energy term is not used in current\nsimulations of galaxy formation and evolution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 13 May 2013 20:00:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-06-17"}
